{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_51_03",
  "title": "小美山愛 3話 父子愛溢れる一杯のラーメン",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "何日もかけて研究を重ね、ついに完成しました！\n『愛マシマシミラクル☆アイドルラーメン』です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After days of research‚ it’s finally complete!\nIt’s the “Extra Love Miracle ☆ Idol Ramen”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "手伝っていただいたお礼と言ってはなんですが\nお二人に食べてもらいたくて！　ささ、遠慮せずに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not much of a way to repay your help‚\nbut I wanted you two to try it! Here‚ help yourself!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ramen-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8633.3333333,
          "startTime": 20.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、お言葉に甘えて。いただきます……うん\nスープに深みがあって、丁寧な飲み口だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I’ll gladly accept your offer. Let’s eat… Hmm.\nThe soup has a lot of depth‚ and a delicate flavor.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "名前は長いけど、お店で出してもおかしくないくらい\n美味しい。名前は長いけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Its name is too long‚ but it’s good enough to sell in a shop.\nIt’s good. The name is too long‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "二回も言わないで下さい！\n最初の名前よりはだいぶ削ったんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t say it twice!\nI already made the name much shorter than the original!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことより、お二人には本当にお世話になりました\nお二人のおかげで隠し味も無事に決まりましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More importantly‚ thank you so much for your help.\nThanks to you‚ I was able to decide on the secret ingredient.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなに……？\n私達の筋トレの何がひらめきに繋がったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really…?\nWhat part of our muscle training inspired you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.933334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "汗だくで、湯気を立ててトレーニングしてる\n千紗さんの手羽……肩甲骨を見たことですかね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While Chisa-san was working out‚ drenched in sweat‚ with steam rising‚\nI saw your wings… I mean‚ shoulder blades‚and it inspired me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0666659039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "今、手羽って言った……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ did you just say wings…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3666671754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "スープに入れたらコクが出て美味しそうで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought putting them in the soup would add depth and be delicious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7333338421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "美味しそう！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Delicious!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7717443705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "それから、しなやかな葵さんのテール……\n引き締まったお尻を見て、スープに入れようと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ Aoi-san’s supple tail…\nSeeing your toned buttocks‚ I knew I had to add it to the soup!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1333501181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "愛は僕で出汁を取ろうと思ったのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Ai was thinking about making broth from me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9666834515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "お二人から手羽とテールを入れる案をいただいたので\nスープに旨味が出たんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got the idea to add wings and tails from you two‚\nso the soup is extra flavorful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.3666834515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "メンバーに食材だと思われてたなんて……\nなんとも言えない気持ちだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My member considered me a food ingredient…\nI don’t know what to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.900019328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "き、きっとそこから思いついただけですよ！\n……多分",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-she probably just got the idea from there!\n…Probably.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8666859946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――誕生日企画当日　開店一時間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The Day of the Birthday Project‚ One Hour Before Opening",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4666819256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.0000183106
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.0000183106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "準備も掃除も完璧……あ、スタッフさん、本日は\nお願いしみゃ……わわわ、噛んじゃいまひた～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The preparations and cleaning are perfect… Oh‚ staff‚\nthank you for your help tewday… W-wawa‚ I stewumbled~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3000183106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.666689555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "確認は何度もしてるし、スタッフさんへの挨拶も\nこれで二回目だよ。さすがに緊張し過ぎかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve checked everything multiple times‚ and this is the second time\nwe’ve greeted the staff. Maybe we're just too nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9333562216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.1000193279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、愛ちゃん。今日のお誕生日企画だけど\n本当に愛ちゃんをお祝いしなくて平気……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Ai-chan. About today’s birthday project…\nAre you sure it’s okay to skip celebrating your birthday…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6000193279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.9666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私は全然！　大好きなお二人と、大好きな実家\nを盛り上げることが出来て、幸せ過ぎるくらいなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? I’m totally fine! I’m already more than happy\nto help out my favorite people and my favorite place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.8999867758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "愛は本当にいい子だね。そんな子にはプレゼントを\nあげよう。ハッピーバースデー、愛。目をつぶって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai is such a good girl. We should give a present\nto this good girl. Happy birthday‚ Ai. Close your eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5999867758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.9999867758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　あ、は、はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? Ah‚ O-okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9999867758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.833298747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "できた！　愛ちゃん、お誕生日おめでとう\n私達から、ヘアメイクのプレゼントだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Done! Happy birthday‚ Ai-chan!\nIt’s a hair and makeup present from us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9999654136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.5333399454
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.433282471
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.8666681925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ～～可愛い！　こんなに可愛くていいのかなー？\n私のために、ありがとうございます！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow This is so cute! Can I really be this cute?\nThank you so much!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.2999562584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.333282471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_03-aoi006.m4a",
